<mvc:View controllerName="workerapp.components.home.controller.Home" 
    xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc" 
    xmlns:core="sap.ui.core" 
    xmlns="sap.m" 
    xmlns:tnt="sap.tnt" 
    xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout" displayBlock="true">
    <Page id="page" showHeader="false" backgroundDesign="Transparent" floatingFooter="true">
        <content>
            <Panel class="sapUiNoContentPadding">
                <l:BlockLayout background="Default">
                    <l:BlockLayoutRow>
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell class="sapUiNoContentPadding" backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeA">
                            <Image src="./images/factory.jpeg" width="100%" height="100%"/>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                    </l:BlockLayoutRow>
                </l:BlockLayout>
            </Panel>
            <Panel class="sapUiNoContentPadding">

                <Title class="sapUiTinyMarginTop" text="{i18n>HOME_TITLE_CARRY_CLOUD}" level="H1" titleStyle="H1" width="100%" textAlign="Center"/>

                <l:BlockLayout background="Default">
                    <l:BlockLayoutRow >
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell class="sapUiNoContentPadding sapUiTinyMarginTop" titleAlignment="Center" backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeA">
                            <FlexBox >
                                <items>
                                    <SlideTile class="sapUiTinyMarginBegin sapUiTinyMarginTop" transitionTime="550" displayTime="5000">
                                        <GenericTile backgroundImage="./images/staffManagement.png" frameType="TwoByOne" press="onPress">
                                            <TileContent footer="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_1_FOOTER}">
                                                <NewsContent contentText="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_1_CONTENT}" subheader="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_1_SUBHEADER}" />
                                            </TileContent>
                                        </GenericTile>
                                        <GenericTile backgroundImage="./images/orderManagement.png" frameType="TwoByOne">
                                            <TileContent footer="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_2_FOOTER}">
                                                <NewsContent contentText="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_2_CONTENT}" subheader="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_2_SUBHEADER}" />
                                            </TileContent>
                                        </GenericTile>
                                    </SlideTile>

                                    <GenericTile class="sapUiTinyMarginBegin sapUiTinyMarginTop" backgroundImage="./images/mainData.png" frameType="TwoByOne" press="onPress">
                                        <TileContent footer="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_3_FOOTER}">
                                            <NewsContent contentText="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_3_CONTENT}" subheader="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_3_SUBHEADER}" />
                                        </TileContent>
                                    </GenericTile>

                                    <SlideTile class="sapUiTinyMarginBegin sapUiTinyMarginTop" transitionTime="250" displayTime="2500">
                                        <GenericTile backgroundImage="./images/staffManagement.png" frameType="TwoByOne" press="onPress">
                                            <TileContent footer="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_4_FOOTER}">
                                                <NewsContent contentText="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_4_CONTENT}" subheader="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_4_SUBHEADER}" />
                                            </TileContent>
                                        </GenericTile>
                                        <GenericTile backgroundImage="./images/orderManagement.png" frameType="TwoByOne">
                                            <TileContent footer="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_5_FOOTER}">
                                                <NewsContent contentText="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_5_CONTENT}" subheader="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_5_SUBHEADER}" />
                                            </TileContent>
                                        </GenericTile>
                                    </SlideTile>

                                    <GenericTile class="sapUiTinyMarginBegin sapUiTinyMarginTop tileLayout" header="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_6_HEADER}" frameType="TwoByOne" press="onPress">
                                        <TileContent footer="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_6_FOOTER}">
                                            <FeedContent contentText="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_6_CONTENT}" subheader="{i18n>HOME_TILE_NEWS_6_SUBHEADER}" value="352" />
                                        </TileContent>
                                    </GenericTile>
                                </items>
                            </FlexBox>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                    </l:BlockLayoutRow>
                    <l:BlockLayoutRow class="sapUiTinyMarginTop">
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell class="sapUiNoContentPadding" backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeD">
                            <Image src="./images/mainData.png" width="100%" height="100%"/>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeC">
                            <l:VerticalLayout class="sapUiContentPadding">
                                <Link class="sapUiDocTitleLink sapMTitle sapMTitleStyleH2 sapUiSelectable wrap sapMTitleMaxWidth sapUiSmallMarginBottom" text="{i18n>HOME_LINK_TEXT_MAINDATA}"/>
                                <Text text="{i18n>HOME_TEXT_MAINDATA}" />
                            </l:VerticalLayout>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                    </l:BlockLayoutRow>
                </l:BlockLayout>
            </Panel>
            <Panel class="sapUiNoContentPadding">

                <Title class="sapUiTinyMarginTop" text="{i18n>HOME_TITLE_TRACE_FACTORY}" level="H1" titleStyle="H1" width="100%" textAlign="Center"/>

                <l:BlockLayout background="Default">
                    <l:BlockLayoutRow >
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell class="sapUiNoContentPadding" backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeB">
                            <Image src="./images/stockManagement.jpg" width="100%" height="100%"/>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeA">
                            <l:VerticalLayout class="sapUiContentPadding">
                                <Link class="sapUiDocTitleLink sapMTitle sapMTitleStyleH2 sapUiSelectable wrap sapMTitleMaxWidth sapUiSmallMarginBottom" text="{i18n>HOME_LINK_TEXT_STOCKMANAGEMENT}"/>
                                <Text text="{i18n>HOME_TEXT_STOCKMANAGEMENT}" />
                            </l:VerticalLayout>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                    </l:BlockLayoutRow>
                    <l:BlockLayoutRow>
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeC">
                            <l:VerticalLayout class="sapUiContentPadding">
                                <Link class="sapUiDocTitleLink sapMTitle sapMTitleStyleH2 sapUiSelectable wrap sapMTitleMaxWidth sapUiSmallMarginBottom" text="{i18n>HOME_LINK_TEXT_ORDERMANAGEMENT}"/>
                                <Text text="{i18n>HOME_TEXT_ORDERMANAGEMENT}"/>
                            </l:VerticalLayout>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell class="sapUiNoContentPadding" backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeD">
                            <Image src="./images/orderManagement.png" width="100%" height="100%"/>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                    </l:BlockLayoutRow>
                </l:BlockLayout>
            </Panel>

            <Panel class="sapUiNoContentPadding">

                <Title class="sapUiTinyMarginTop" text="{i18n>HOME_TITLE_TEXT_STAFFMANAGEMENT}" level="H1" titleStyle="H1" width="100%" textAlign="Center"/>

                <l:BlockLayout background="Default">
                    <l:BlockLayoutRow >
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell class="sapUiNoContentPadding" backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeC">
                            <Image src="./images/staffManagement.png" width="100%" height="100%"/>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                    </l:BlockLayoutRow>
                    <l:BlockLayoutRow >
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeA">
                            <l:VerticalLayout class="sapUiContentPadding">
                                <Link class="sapUiDocTitleLink sapMTitle sapMTitleStyleH2 sapUiSelectable wrap sapMTitleMaxWidth sapUiSmallMarginBottom" text="{i18n>HOME_LINK_TEXT_STAFFMANAGEMENT_CREATE}"/>
                                <Text text="{i18n>HOME_TEXT_STAFFMANAGEMENT_CREATE}" />
                            </l:VerticalLayout>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeC">
                            <l:VerticalLayout class="sapUiContentPadding">
                                <Link class="sapUiDocTitleLink sapMTitle sapMTitleStyleH2 sapUiSelectable wrap sapMTitleMaxWidth sapUiSmallMarginBottom" text="{i18n>HOME_LINK_TEXT_STAFFMANAGEMENT_ORDERMANAGEMENT}"/>
                                <Text text="{i18n>HOME_TEXT_STAFFMANAGEMENT_ORDERMANAGEMENT}" />
                            </l:VerticalLayout>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeB">
                            <l:VerticalLayout class="sapUiContentPadding">
                                <Link class="sapUiDocTitleLink sapMTitle sapMTitleStyleH2 sapUiSelectable wrap sapMTitleMaxWidth sapUiSmallMarginBottom" text="{i18n>HOME_LINK_TEXT_STAFFMANAGEMENT_PRODUCTION}"/>
                                <Text text="{i18n>HOME_TEXT_STAFFMANAGEMENT_PRODUCTION}" />
                            </l:VerticalLayout>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeD">
                            <l:VerticalLayout class="sapUiContentPadding">
                                <Link class="sapUiDocTitleLink sapMTitle sapMTitleStyleH2 sapUiSelectable wrap sapMTitleMaxWidth sapUiSmallMarginBottom" text="{i18n>HOME_LINK_TEXT_STAFFMANAGEMENT_CONSUMPTION}"/>
                                <Text text="{i18n>HOME_TEXT_STAFFMANAGEMENT_CONSUMPTION}" />
                            </l:VerticalLayout>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                    </l:BlockLayoutRow>
                </l:BlockLayout>
            </Panel>
            <Panel class="sapUiNoContentPadding">

                <Title class="sapUiTinyMarginTop" text="{i18n>HOME_TITLE_TEXT_COMMUNITY}" level="H1" titleStyle="H1" width="100%" textAlign="Center"/>

                <l:BlockLayout class="sapUiContentPadding" background="Default">
                    <l:BlockLayoutRow>
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeA">
                            <l:HorizontalLayout >
                                <core:Icon src="sap-icon://collaborate" size="2.5rem" color="Default"></core:Icon>
                                <Link class="sapUiDocTitleLink sapMTitle sapMTitleStyleH2 sapUiSelectable sapMTitleNoWrap sapMTitleMaxWidth sapUiSmallMargin sapUiNoMarginBottom sapUiNoMarginEnd" text="{i18n>HOME_LINK_TEXT_HUMAN_RESOURCES}"/>
                            </l:HorizontalLayout>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeC">
                            <l:HorizontalLayout>
                                <Image src="./images/logo_youtube.png" width="2.5rem" class="sapMImg sapUiTinyMarginTop"/>
                                <Link class="sapUiDocTitleLink sapMTitle sapMTitleStyleH2 sapUiSelectable sapMTitleNoWrap sapMTitleMaxWidth sapUiSmallMargin sapUiNoMarginBottom sapUiNoMarginEnd" text="{i18n>HOME_LINK_TEXT_YOUTUBE}"/>
                            </l:HorizontalLayout>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeB">
                            <l:HorizontalLayout >
                                <Image src="./images/logo_twitter.png" width="2.5rem" class="sapMImg sapUiTinyMarginTop"/>
                                <Link class="sapUiDocTitleLink sapMTitle sapMTitleStyleH2 sapUiSelectable sapMTitleNoWrap sapMTitleMaxWidth sapUiSmallMargin sapUiNoMarginBottom sapUiNoMarginEnd" text="{i18n>HOME_LINK_TEXT_TWITTER}"/>
                            </l:HorizontalLayout>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                        <l:BlockLayoutCell backgroundColorSet="ColorSet11" backgroundColorShade="ShadeD">
                            <l:HorizontalLayout>
                                <Image src="./images/linkedin.png" width="2.5rem" class="sapMImg sapUiTinyMarginTop"/>
                                <Link class="sapUiDocTitleLink sapMTitle sapMTitleStyleH2 sapUiSelectable sapMTitleNoWrap sapMTitleMaxWidth sapUiSmallMargin sapUiNoMarginBottom sapUiNoMarginEnd" text="{i18n>HOME_LINK_TEXT_LINKEDIN}"/>
                            </l:HorizontalLayout>
                        </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                    </l:BlockLayoutRow>
                </l:BlockLayout>
            </Panel>

            <l:BlockLayout>
                <l:BlockLayoutRow>
                    <l:BlockLayoutCell class="customFooterCell">
                            
                    </l:BlockLayoutCell>
                </l:BlockLayoutRow>
            </l:BlockLayout>
            
        </content>
    </Page>
</mvc:View>